Extra functionality
===================

couch_log.erl
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

A plugin that logs the messages to a CouchDB database. It requires CouchBeam_.
To compile first clone and compile CouchBeam_::

 cd extra
 git clone git://github.com/benoitc/couchbeam.git
 cd couchbeam
 make
 cd ..
 erlc -o ../ebin/plugins -I couchbeam/include couch_log.erl

then to use the plugin, you'll have to add the "ebin/" directories to the path
of your erlang process too::

  erl -pa ebin -pa extra/couchbeam/ebin -pa extra/couchbeam/deps/*/ebin



.. _CouchBeam: http://benoitc.github.com/couchbeam/
